c: 39
v: 71
t: "And by TROOPS shall the unbelievers be driven towards Hell, until when they reach it, its gates shall be opened, and its keepers shall say to them, \"Came not apostles from among yourselves to you, reciting to you the signs of your Lord, and warning you of the meeting with Him on this your day?\" They shall say, \"Yes.\" But just is the sentence of punishment on the unbelievers"